description_zh:

<「不死の黒蛇」>の【灼熱の息吹】の持続ダメージが上昇

<color=#EC1F1FFF>Condition: </color>

<Emperor's Blade, Pursuer> [Dominion] ASPD reduction increased

<Andoain the Martyr> [Light Unto Sufferers] dodge and damage reduction effect increased
